{"tid":1717541,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［緊急］11.13 重傷傷者資訊整合","createTime":"2019-11-13T15:37:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T18:11:53.000Z","uid":266685,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":75,"replies":[{"pid":"489678363916dc2433dbeed76ce920109097116f","tid":1717541,"uid":266685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T15:37:45.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">請全世界一齊跟進所有重傷手足既情況 被自殺既一個都唔可以再多</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n1.<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SR6Npjw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSR6Npjw.jpg&h=81b96f82&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n樓豬唔清楚手足送左去邊間醫院 麻煩大家報料<br />\n<br />\n2.<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wVWqaZM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwVWqaZM.png&h=126000c5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ecE7pjR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FecE7pjR.png&h=12f20f74&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n傷者歲數：15<br />\n受傷地點：天水圍（請再fc <strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">樓豬唔肯定</span></strong>）<br />\n送院：屯門醫院<br />\n傷勢：skull fracture（顱骨骨折）<br />\n手足有流CSF - cerebrospinal fluid = 腦部嚴重受創既sign<br />\n做緊手術 <br />\n（source：tg channel 及facebook video）<br />\n<br />\n3.<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uiNprzn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuiNprzn.jpg&h=c734213c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jgFRQ03.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjgFRQ03.jpg&h=f4fd32a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n傷者資料：全部不詳<br />\n受傷地點：荃灣葵福路嘉里物流外<br />\n送院：仁濟醫院<br />\n情況簡述：最早目擊者時間為2233 被發現係葵福路 嘉里物流外 無心跳 做緊cpr 同aed  手有復習性骨折 已上白車 白車車牌 a137<br />\n<br />\nFA 指無目擊者 但佢有急救牌 睇骨折程度 似高處跌下 更似被斬<br />\n（Source：全部來自tg channel）<br />\n<br />\n麻煩大家一齊跟進<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c1c0a5c494a06fc34bc495f79600146ce893ba1"